headline: Procore And United Rentals Link Telematics As Shares Trade Below Targets
summary: Procore Technologies and United Rentals announced a new partnership that connects rental equipment telematics data directly into Procore's construction management platform. The integration is designed to give shared customers better visibility into equipment usage, location, and status across active jobs. The collaboration aims to support AI driven optimization of construction project workflows by tying field data more tightly to project planning and execution. Procore Technologies...
